Package <Unnamed>

Interface Summary
MazeGenerator Interface for maze generators.
 

Class Summary
Controller Controller for player in the maze.
Enemy Enemy against player of the maze.
Game Game class that setups maze and in-game screens in preparation for a game.
GameFrame GUI class for the game interface.
GameManager System managing game flow.
InstructionFrame The Instruction Frame contains the instructions of the game for the user
Maze Contains the board of the maze.
MazeFrame GUI class for the maze game.
OptionPanel Class containing JPanel for options for Character, Difficulty selection and setting Name
Player Player of the maze game.
PrimMazeGenerator Maze generator using Prim's algorithm.
Run The Maze Runner (May 2014).
Sprite Create a Sprite based on provided string identifier of gif image in sprite directory.
Tile Tile Class for maze representation.
TileEdge Edge consisting of three adjacent tiles on the board of the maze.
